{"tid":625031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"採訪蘿莉性愛娃娃　BBC男記者當場哭了","createTime":"2018-04-11T06:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T05:38:09.000Z","uid":72009,"like":193,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd9d5d0dd4e695ea1a65ab82ac517cdccabe2e4","tid":625031,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"英國《BBC》男記者楊恩(James Young)日前到日本東京採訪性愛娃娃工廠，但當他看到娃娃的半成品時，竟然當場飆淚。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，當楊恩看到性愛娃娃的半成品時，卻突然「悲從中來」，因為楊恩覺得，這些娃娃的尺寸，實在太像小蘿莉，讓他不禁聯想到戀童癖，讓他太震撼。雖然楊恩嘴巴不說，只在現場哭泣，但工廠主人大川廣(Hiro Okawa)了解他的心情，「我知道你想說什麼」。<br />\n<br />\n大川廣強調，製作這些蘿莉尺寸的性愛娃娃，在日本並不犯法，至於娃娃的「年齡」，也保留給使用者去想像。但大川也承認，這些蘿莉性愛娃娃確實會引起眾人反感，引起負面評論，因此這些娃娃僅在日本販售，並不會外銷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180411/1332324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180411%2F1332324&d=kQgFSJP9XBHiOkgzvsGqHi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fc8230d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180411%2F1332324&h=1ed3592e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180411/1332324</a><br />\n<br />\n怕了左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0187f0d05fb1029831e0a7e28b49844bf52c98","tid":625031,"uid":53577,"like":172,"dislike":12,"score":160,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"楊恩： LGBT +人獸我樣樣啱，但你幻想蘿莉就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a68829807f1aac1043c9e1e015cbc4408ac2159","tid":625031,"uid":157362,"like":65,"dislike":4,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2dd362f9740daf7ae7ba642db81e328dacd4958d","tid":625031,"uid":160807,"like":181,"dislike":10,"score":171,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:30:48.000Z","msg":"佢係開心到咸姐"},{"pid":"3546cf79c9bc30308757bd66d427030135cf54e2","tid":625031,"uid":24805,"like":96,"d