"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"人地都未講, 個老闆就認叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd40fc5661a97c9f7b57ecabe3edde499f79f97d","tid":625031,"uid":24805,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"James Young自己都寫係太震撼有呢種需求，而個需求係外間不能接受，個公仔只係令用家繼續困死自己係蘿莉愛 － <br />\n<br />\n即係，我不能接受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFor me it was impossible to detach myself from the thought that very young looking dolls have been confiscated in the UK for being indecent.<br />\n<br />\nAll of my thoughts regarding how adult sex dolls could affect the behaviour of users quickly translated into abuse scenarios. If adult dolls could encourage objectification of women, younger looking sex dolls would be no different.<br />\n<br />\nI felt so afraid that producing these dolls might only let users live in an imaginary world that reinforces that it&rsquo;s okay. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/tech/factory-making-child-sex-robots-12309392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Ftech%2Ffactory-making-child-sex-robots-12309392&d=kQgFSJP9XBHiOkgzvsGqHi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9caaf920\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/tech/factory-making-child-sex-robots-12309392</a>"},{"pid":"19261fc83aaf4caaa18c4805a9d7848d88c451e3","tid":625031,"uid":52459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"問廠長有無discount"},{"pid":"012be3fee2ef24a99f9335a348d32f084ad23f14","tid":625031,"uid":1425,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"十足十啲中文閱讀理解咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76447b475c5ccb2f4716bc411f45ba3bd85c5548","tid":625031,"uid":160807,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"b1bee48e0d7f2d470125